   <text>
      <body>         
         <div type="panelGrp" xml:id="pg_155">
            
            <cbml:panel n="1" characters="#Merle #Griffin #Bogard">
               <note resp="https://orcid.org/0009-0002-7009-7250" type="panelDesc">Merle, spellcasting from his spellbook, is interupted by the DM, Griffin. Griffin pops up in the top right corner from his mysterious yellow bubble.</note>
               <cbml:balloon type="speech" who="#Griffin">IF I WERE YOU, I WOULD TRY TO DO IT UNDER YOUR BREATH.</cbml:balloon>
               <cbml:balloon type="speech" who="#Merle">OH.</cbml:balloon>
            </cbml:panel>
            
            <cbml:panel n="2" characters="#Merle" ana="#">
               <note resp="#" type="panelDesc">Merle thinking outloud to himself while still holding his spell book.</note>
               <cbml:balloon type="speech" who="#Merle" style="font-bold">HANG ON... I HAVE TO SNEEZE. AAH-</cbml:balloon>
            </cbml:panel>
            
            <cbml:panel n="3" characters="#" >
               <note resp="#" type="panelDesc">Merle scrunching his face up over his open spellbook.</note>
            </cbml:panel>
            
            <cbml:panel n="4" characters="#" style="hue-pink">
               <note resp="#" type="panelDesc"></note>
               <cbml:balloon type="speech" who="#Merle">Merele casting the spell Zone of Truth. The entire panel is filled with a pink hue, flowers, and sparkles.</cbml:balloon>
               <sound type="sneeze" style="fontsize-large fontcolor-pink ">ACHOOZONE OF TRUTH</sound>
            </cbml:panel>
            
            <cbml:panel n="5" characters="#" style="hue-pink">
               <note resp="#" type="panelDesc">Everyone is looking at the pink light and sparkles while Merle smiles. This art of this panel fills the entire page, goind under the other panels, giving the appearence of a lack of borders for this panel.</note>
            </cbml:panel>
            
            <cbml:panel n="6" characters="#" style="hue-pink">
               <note resp="#" type="panelDesc">Bogard crosses his arms and Merle smiles as they talk to each other. The entire panel is in a pink hue.</note>
               <cbml:balloon type="speech" who="#Bogard">DID YOU JUST CASE SOME SORT OF MAGIC SPELL ON ME?</cbml:balloon>
               <cbml:balloon type="speech" who="#Merle">YES! I CAST ZONE OF TRUTH WHICH FORCES YOU TO SAY ONLY TRUE STATEMENTS!</cbml:balloon>
               <cbml:balloon type="speech" who="#Merle">NO ONE WITHIN THE AREA OF EFECT CAN RESIST ITS POWER!</cbml:balloon>
            </cbml:panel>
            
            <cbml:panel n="7" characters="#" style="hue-pink">
               <note resp="#" type="panelDesc">Griffin pops in the left top corner eacting popcorn as he watches Merle and Bogard talk to each other; the yellow background of Griffin's area stands out against the pink hue of everything else.</note>
               <cbml:balloon type="speech" who="#Griffin">INCLUDING YOURSELF.</cbml:balloon>
               <cbml:balloon type="speech" who="#Merle">INCLUDING ME-</cbml:balloon>
            </cbml:panel>
               
            <cbml:panel n="8" characters="#" style="hue-pink">
                  <note resp="#" type="panelDesc">Merle Slaps his temple as he speaks, still in pink hue.</note>
                  <cbml:balloon type="speech" who="#Merle">DAMMIT.</cbml:balloon>
                  <sound>SLAP.</sound>
                  </cbml:panel>

